  time_bucket('1d', h.datetime) as time,
    sum(h.strategist_wnative_amount) as strategist_amount,
    sum(h.beefy_wnative_amount * 0.86) as bifi_stakers_amount,
    sum(h.beefy_wnative_amount * 0.14) as bifi_treasury_amount
FROM
  data_raw.vault_harvest_1d_ts h
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(h.datetime)
  and h.chain = '$chain'
  and h.vault_id in ($vault_id)
group by 1
order by 1

    'WMATIC', -- polygon
    'WSYS' -- syscoin
  )
  group by 1
)
SELECT
  time_bucket('1d', h.datetime) as time,
    sum(sum(h.strategist_wnative_amount) * avg(usd_value)) over (order by time_bucket('1d', h.datetime)) as strategist_amount,
    sum(sum(h.beefy_wnative_amount * 0.86) * avg(usd_value)) over (order by time_bucket('1d', h.datetime)) as bifi_stakers_amount,
    sum(sum(h.beefy_wnative_amount * 0.14) * avg(usd_value)) over (order by time_bucket('1d', h.datetime)) as bifi_treasury_amount
FROM
  data_raw.vault_harvest_1d_ts h
     left join price_1d p on p.oracle_id = 
        case 
            when h.chain = 'arbitrum' then 'WETH'
            when h.chain = 'aurora' then 'WETH'
            when h.chain = 'avax' then 'AVAX'
            when h.chain = 'bsc' then 'WBNB'
            when h.chain = 'celo' then 'CELO'
            when h.chain = 'cronos' then 'WCRO'
            when h.chain = 'emerald' then 'ROSE'
            when h.chain = 'fantom' then 'WFTM'
            when h.chain = 'fuse' then 'WFUSE'
            when h.chain = 'harmony' then 'ONE'
            when h.chain = 'heco' then 'WHT'
            when h.chain = 'metis' then 'METIS'
            when h.chain = 'moonbeam' then 'WGLMR'
            when h.chain = 'moonriver' then 'MOVR'
            when h.chain = 'optimism' then 'WETH'
            when h.chain = 'polygon' then 'WMATIC'
            when h.chain = 'syscoin' then 'WSYS'
            else null
        end
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(h.datetime)
  and chain = '$chain'
  and vault_id in ($vault_id)
group by 1
order by 1
